Title: Invicta Men's Speedway Chronograph 200m Two Toned Stainless Steel Watch 3644
Description: A superior mix of mechanics and materials, this Invicta men's chronograph watch features a round blue dial, luminous hands and hour markers and date window between 4 and 5 o'clock positions. All of these are framed in a stainless steel case, unidirectional gold plated bezel, screw down crown and scratch resistant mineral crystal. It also offers a two toned (silver and gold plated) stainless steel band secured with foldover safety clasp, Japan quartz movement and water resistance up to 200 meters / 660 feet. Chronograph Round blue dial Luminous hands and hour markers Date window between 4 and 5 o'clock Stainless steel case Unidirectional gold plated bezel Screw down crown Scratch resistant mineral crystal Two toned (silver and gold plated) stainless steel band with foldover safety clasp Japan quartz movement Water resistance up to 200m/660ft Case diameter: 39.5 mm Case thickness: 13 mm Band width: 20 mm Band length: 205 mm
